			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">To answer the original poster's question (elemental items that will probably not be replaced by Time loot), here are my picks, in no particular order:
<br />

<br />
1. Simple Ring of Purity (Xegony)
<br />
2. Magi'kots Tiara of Convergence (Mold)
<br />
3. Magi'kot's Sleeves of Convergence (Mold)
<br />

<br />
Some people prefer Elemental Legs over Quarm legs, but I like Quarm legs myself.  Everything else you can get in the Elemental Planes will likely be replaced in Plane of Time without much to think about.  
<br />

<br />
Also, as a poster said earlier, there is another ring you can get in the new VP now that is almost as good as Simple Ring of Purity.
<br />

<br />
Of course, my picks are based on the assumption that you will get everything you want of Plane of Time, and that is not always a realistic way of thought.  If you are not going to be spending a lot of time in Plane of Time, the list might be a bit larger =)<br />_________________<br /><br><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=140907"><b><i>Platinus Dimas</i></b></a><br><a href="http://www.diligenceguild.com">Diligence</a><br><a href="http://p077.ezboard.com/bteamprimal82955">Team Primal</a></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
